__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.seen_hashes.txt
ledger/.seen_hashes.txt
.env
.claude/

# Original-form capture: large forensic binaries (WARC, raw wget HTML, video).
# These are kept in off-platform custody (see cases/*/evidence/CAPTURE-RUNBOOK.md);
# the integrity records (manifest.json, sha256sums.txt), PDFs and screenshots ARE
# committed. To deliberately commit one ignored artifact: git add -f <path>.
**/evidence/*/original/*.warc
**/evidence/*/original/*.html
**/evidence/*/original/*.mp4
**/evidence/*/original/*.mkv
**/evidence/*/original/*.webm
**/evidence/*/original/*.m4a
**/evidence/*/original/*.m4v
